JSONPresenter in cli/output/json.go. Uses encoding/json with struct-driven field ordering and HTML escaping disabled for readability. Per-method serialization per <ref spec="output.json_schema">the JSON schema</ref>. The marshal helper uses json.Encoder with SetEscapeHTML(false) and trims the trailing newline. Todo items carry a "kind" discriminator ("link", "refChain", "cascade", "refAdded", "refRemoved", "brokenRef") so JSON consumers can dispatch on drift kind. See <ref spec="output.json_mode">JSON mode</ref>.